<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>PENALBOT — Premium Penalty Signal Intelligence</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&family=Bricolage+Grotesque:opsz,wght@12..96,400;12..96,500;12..96,700;12..96,800&family=Archivo+Black:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#050509;--s1:rgba(255,255,255,.055);--s2:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  --b:rgba(255,255,255,.10);--t:#f4eeff;--m:#bfb2dc;--m2:#8a809e;
  --p:#b92eff;--p2:#7c3bff;--a:#ff48d4;--g:#42f5a0;--g2:#16382b;
  --r:26px;--rr:999px;--content:1200px;
  --glow:0 0 80px rgba(185,46,255,.22);
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{
  font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;color:var(--t);background:var(--bg);
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(circle at 12% 12%,rgba(185,46,255,.22) 0,transparent 28%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 88% 18%,rgba(255,72,212,.15) 0,transparent 24%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 50% 90%,rgba(124,59,255,.18) 0,transparent 26%);
  overflow-x:hidden;min-height:100vh;
}
body::before{
  content:"";position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;
  background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.018) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.018) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:46px 46px;
  mask-image:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 40%,black 38%,transparent 90%);
}
a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
img{display:block;max-width:100%}
.wrap{width:min(calc(100% - 32px),var(--content));margin:0 auto}

/* ─── NAV ─── */
.nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;backdrop-filter:blur(18px);background:rgba(5,5,9,.6);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);box-shadow:0 1px 0 rgba(185,46,255,.10)}
.nav-in{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:20px;padding:16px 0}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:13px;font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:18px}
.logo-wrap{width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(185,46,255,.35);flex-shrink:0}
.logo-wrap img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.logo-pill{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.09);
  border-radius:var(--rr);padding:7px 10px;
}
.logo-pill img{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover}
.nav-links{
  display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.09);
  padding:7px;border-radius:var(--rr)
}
.nav-links a{
  color:var(--m);padding:9px 20px;border-radius:var(--rr);
  font-size:14px;font-weight:600;transition:.22s ease;letter-spacing:.01em;
}
.nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.active{color:#fff;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:13px 22px;border-radius:var(--rr);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;border:1px solid transparent;transition:.22s ease;cursor:pointer}
.btn-p{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--p),var(--a));color:#fff;box-shadow:0 10px 36px rgba(185,46,255,.3);padding:13px 22px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.02em}
.btn-p:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);filter:brightness(1.07)}
.btn-s{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);color:var(--t);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.10)}
.btn-tg{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;
  padding:13px 20px;border-radius:999px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
  color:#fff;transition:.22s ease;letter-spacing:.02em;cursor:pointer;
  text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;
}
.btn-tg:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}
.btn-tg svg{width:17px;height:17px;flex-shrink:0}
.btn-s:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.09)}

/* ─── HERO ─── */
.hero{padding:68px 0 36px}
.hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:28px;align-items:start}
.eyebrow{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  padding:10px 14px;border-radius:var(--rr);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);
  color:#e4d4ff;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:18px
}
.pulse{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--g);animation:pulse 1.8s infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(66,245,160,.5)}70%{box-shadow:0 0 0 14px rgba(66,245,160,0)}100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(66,245,160,0)}}
h1{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(46px,6.5vw,90px);line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-.055em;max-width:10ch}
.grad{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff 0%,#edcaff 35%,#ff80e0 72%,#fff);-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}
.hero-sub{margin-top:22px;max-width:58ch;color:var(--m);font-size:17px;line-height:1.8}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:14px;margin-top:26px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.hero-note{margin-top:10px;color:var(--m2);font-size:13px}

/* ─── METRICS ─── */
.metrics{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:32px}
.metric{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.09);
  border-radius:20px;padding:24px 22px;
  opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:.6s ease;
}
.metric.visible{opacity:1;transform:none}
.metric strong{display:block;font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,50px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.04em;color:#fff}
.metric small{color:var(--m);font-size:13px;margin-top:4px;display:block}

/* ─── HERO RIGHT ─── */
.hero-right{display:grid;gap:16px}

/* ─── TERMINAL ─── */
.terminal{
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(6,12,9,.96),rgba(4,9,6,.97));
  border:1px solid rgba(66,245,160,.18);border-radius:24px;
  padding:0;overflow:hidden;
}
.term-bar{
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:12px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(66,245,160,.12);
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)
}
.term-dots{display:flex;gap:7px}
.term-dots span{width:11px;height:11px;border-radius:50%}
.term-dots span:nth-child(1){background:#ff5f57}
.term-dots span:nth-child(2){background:#ffbd2e}
.term-dots span:nth-child(3){background:#28ca41}
.term-title{font-size:12px;color:#7cf5b8;letter-spacing:.10em;text-transform:uppercase}
.term-body{padding:18px;min-height:220px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.code-out{font-family:ui-monospace,'Cascadia Code',Menlo,monospace;font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#5be8a6}
.code-line{display:block;opacity:0;animation:fadein .12s forwards}
@keyframes fadein{to{opacity:1}}
.code-line.green{color:#42f5a0;font-weight:700}
.code-cursor{display:inline-block;width:8px;height:14px;background:var(--g);animation:blink .8s step-end infinite;vertical-align:middle;margin-left:3px;border-radius:2px}
@keyframes blink{50%{opacity:0}}

/* ─── TELEGRAM ─── */
.telegram{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#10111f,#0b0c16);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);border-radius:26px;overflow:hidden}
.tg-bar{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:14px 18px;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)
}
.tg-ava{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;overflow:hidden;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14)}
.tg-ava img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.tg-info strong{display:block;font-size:15px}
.tg-info span{color:var(--g);font-size:12px}
.tg-msgs{padding:18px;display:grid;gap:0}
.tg-bubble{
  max-width:85%;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:18px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.65;
  border-top-left-radius:6px;
  opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px) scale(.97);
  animation:bubblepop .45s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1) forwards;
}
@keyframes bubblepop{to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
.tg-bubble .row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:10px}
.tg-bubble .row img{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:7px;object-fit:cover}
.tg-bubble .row strong{font-size:14px;color:#f0e4ff}
.signal-inner{
  margin-top:10px;padding:11px 13px;border-radius:13px;
  background:rgba(66,245,160,.10);border:1px solid rgba(66,245,160,.22);color:#d0ffec;font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.7
}
.signal-inner strong{color:#42f5a0;display:block;margin-bottom:5px}
.tg-time{display:block;text-align:right;margin-top:8px;color:var(--m2);font-size:11px}

/* ─── SECTIONS ─── */
section{padding:50px 0 20px}
.sec-head{display:grid;grid-template-columns:.9fr 1.1fr;gap:20px;align-items:end;margin-bottom:24px}
.sec-head h2{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,54px);line-height:1;letter-spacing:-.04em}
.sec-head p{color:var(--m);line-height:1.8}
.grid3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:17px}
.card{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.09);
  border-radius:22px;padding:24px;
  transition:border-color .25s,transform .25s;
}
.card:hover{border-color:rgba(185,46,255,.35);transform:translateY(-3px)}
.tag{
  display:inline-flex;margin-bottom:13px;padding:7px 11px;border-radius:var(--rr);
  background:rgba(185,46,255,.14);border:1px solid rgba(185,46,255,.24);
  color:#eddcff;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700
}
.card h3{font-size:19px;margin-bottom:9px;font-weight:700;font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;letter-spacing:-.02em}
.card p{color:var(--m);line-height:1.75;font-size:15px}

/* ─── TECH SPLIT ─── */
.tech-split{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;gap:20px;align-items:start}

/* ─── PRICING ─── */
.pricegrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:17px}
.pcard{
  position:relative;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.09);
  border-radius:26px;padding:26px
}
.pcard.star{border-color:rgba(255,72,212,.42);box-shadow:0 18px 56px rgba(185,46,255,.18);transform:translateY(-8px)}
.badge2{
  position:absolute;top:14px;right:14px;padding:7px 12px;border-radius:var(--rr);
  font-size:11px;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--p),var(--a));
}
.pcard h3{font-size:22px;font-weight:700}
.pcard>p{margin-top:7px;color:var(--m);font-size:14px;line-height:1.7}
.pricetag{margin-top:14px;font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:48px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.05em}
.pricetag small{font-size:16px;color:var(--m);font-family:Inter,sans-serif}
ul{list-style:none;display:grid;gap:11px;margin-top:16px}
li{position:relative;padding-left:17px;color:#efe6ff;font-size:14px}
li::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:0;top:9px;width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--p),var(--a))}

/* ─── CTA ─── */
.cta-band{
  margin:44px 0 66px;padding:28px 32px;border-radius:28px;
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(185,46,255,.16),rgba(255,72,212,.08));
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.cta-band h3{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:28px}
.cta-band p{color:var(--m);line-height:1.7;max-width:58ch;font-size:15px;margin-top:8px}

/* ─── DECORATIVE LOGO FLOAT ─── */
.logo-float{
  position:absolute;width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;
  opacity:.18;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);pointer-events:none;
}

/* ─── FOOTER ─── */
footer{padding:18px 0 52px;color:var(--m2);font-size:13px}


/* V4 refinements */
.hero-sub{font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.82;color:var(--m);max-width:56ch}
.eyebrow{border:1px solid rgba(185,46,255,.22);background:rgba(185,46,255,.08);color:#e6d4ff;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.015em}
.card{border-radius:20px;padding:26px}
.tag{font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.14em}
.metric small{font-size:12.5px;letter-spacing:.01em;color:var(--m2);margin-top:5px}
.pcard{border-radius:24px;padding:28px}
.pcard.star .badge2{font-size:10px;padding:6px 11px}
.nav-in{padding:14px 0}

/* ─── SCROLL REVEAL ─── */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:.65s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1)}
.reveal.on{opacity:1;transform:none}

@media(max-width:960px){.hero-grid,.sec-head,.grid3,.tech-split,.pricegrid,.metrics{grid-template-columns:1fr}.pcard.star{transform:none}.nav-links{display:none}.btn-tg span.tg-label{display:none}}
@media(max-width:680px){.hero{padding-top:36px}h1{max-width:12ch}.hero-btns{flex-direction:column;gap:10px}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<header class="nav">
<div class="wrap nav-in">
  <a href="#top" class="brand">
    <span class="logo-wrap"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="PENALBOT" width="46" height="46"/></span>
    <span style="
  font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
  font-size:20px;
  font-weight:400;
  letter-spacing:.12em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffffff 0%,#e8d0ff 45%,#ff85e0 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip:text;
  background-clip:text;
  color:transparent;
  line-height:1;
  padding-bottom:1px;
">PENALBOT</span>
  </a>
  <nav class="nav-links">
    <a class="active" href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#technology">Technology</a>
    <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
  </nav>
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
    <a class="btn-tg" href="https://t.me/penalbotteam" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 240 240" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M120 0C53.73 0 0 53.73 0 120s53.73 120 120 120 120-53.73 120-120S186.27 0 120 0zm59.14 81.94l-20.26 95.52c-1.49 6.6-5.39 8.23-10.92 5.12l-30.18-22.23-14.57 14.02c-1.61 1.61-2.96 2.96-6.07 2.96l2.17-30.72 55.92-50.52c2.43-2.16-.53-3.36-3.77-1.2L77.3 142.43l-29.7-9.28c-6.46-2.02-6.59-6.46 1.34-9.57l116.22-44.82c5.38-1.95 10.09 1.31 8.98 3.18z" fill="white"/></svg>
      CONTACT
    </a>
    <a class="btn btn-p" href="#pricing">Get Access</a>
  </div>
</div>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="top">
<div class="wrap hero-grid">

  <!-- LEFT -->
  <div>
    <div class="eyebrow"><span class="pulse"></span> Premium Penalty Signal Platform</div>
    <h1><span class="grad">Precision signals</span> for penalty markets</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      PENALBOT is a multi-factor engine that cross-references referee intelligence, team pressure dynamics, defensive vulnerability and market pricing to surface only the highest-conviction penalty setups — delivered instantly on Telegram.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a class="btn btn-p" href="#pricing">Join PENALBOT</a>
      <a class="btn btn-s" href="#technology">Explore the stack</a>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-note">Stripe checkout → automatic Telegram access onboarding.</p>

    <div class="metrics">
      <div class="metric">
        <strong data-target="100000" data-prefix="+" data-sep="true">0</strong>
        <small>matches analysed</small>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <strong data-target="62.3" data-suffix="%" data-dec="1">0</strong>
        <small>win rate</small>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <strong data-target="70.5" data-suffix="%" data-dec="1">0</strong>
        <small>projected ROI</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- RIGHT -->
  <div class="hero-right">

    <!-- TERMINAL -->
    <div class="terminal">
      <div class="term-bar">
        <div class="term-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <div class="term-title">penalbot-engine · live scan</div>
        <div style="color:#42f5a0;font-size:11px">● running</div>
      </div>
      <div class="term-body">
        <div class="code-out" id="termOut"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TELEGRAM -->
    <div class="telegram">
      <div class="tg-bar">
        <div class="tg-ava"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="PENALBOT" width="40" height="40"/></div>
        <div class="tg-info">
          <strong>PENALBOT Premium</strong>
          <span>● online · live signals</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tg-msgs" id="tgMsgs"></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="sec-head reveal">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>PENALBOT is not a generic tipster. It is a specialised signal layer built specifically around one micro-market — the penalty in top European football. The system synthesises referee data, squad behaviour, market inefficiencies and probabilistic modelling to push only the most compelling setups.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid3">
    <article class="card reveal">
      <div class="tag">Positioning</div>
      <h3>Niche market dominance</h3>
      <p>Focused on a vertical rarely treated seriously. Penalty specialisation delivers asymmetric information advantage and a clearly differentiated product narrative.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card reveal">
      <div class="tag">Distribution</div>
      <h3>Telegram-native delivery</h3>
      <p>Signals arrive directly in your private channel — formatted, readable, instantly actionable. Zero friction between discovery, payment and live use.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card reveal">
      <div class="tag">Philosophy</div>
      <h3>Filter more, push less</h3>
      <p>The premium positioning rests on scarcity and clarity. Fewer signals, higher conviction. The engine is tuned to refuse ambiguous setups.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- TECHNOLOGY -->
<section id="technology">
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="sec-head reveal">
    <h2>Technology</h2>
    <p>A composite quantitative architecture: Referee Intelligence Layer, Penalty Pressure Index, Defensive Vulnerability Score, probabilistic calibration, signal scoring and bankroll-aware stake staging — running across 6 leagues simultaneously.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid3" style="margin-bottom:18px">
    <article class="card reveal">
      <div class="tag">Layer 01</div>
      <h3>Referee Intelligence</h3>
      <p>Referee profiling, penalty frequency, strictness variance, contextual home/away bias, weighted arbitral factor in final signal score.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card reveal">
      <div class="tag">Layer 02</div>
      <h3>Pressure & Vulnerability</h3>
      <p>Penalty Pressure Index (PPI) and Defensive Vulnerability Score (DVS) measure offensive threat and defensive fragility — the two primary setup drivers.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card reveal">
      <div class="tag">Layer 03</div>
      <h3>Market Synthesis</h3>
      <p>Internal probability is confronted with live bookmaker pricing. Signal is only pushed when edge remains coherent after market adjustments.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- PRICING -->
<section id="pricing">
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="sec-head reveal">
    <h2>Pricing</h2>
    <p>Three tiers to match different levels of engagement. Next step: connect Stripe Checkout + webhook to automate Telegram access after confirmed payment.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pricegrid">
    <article class="pcard reveal">
      <h3>Starter</h3>
      <p>Entry-level access to discover the product and first signals.</p>
      <div class="pricetag">€9.99<small>/mo</small></div>
      <ul>
        <li>Essential signal access</li>
        <li>Limited league coverage</li>
        <li>Private Telegram channel</li>
        <li>Standard support</li>
      </ul>
      <div style="margin-top:22px"><a class="btn btn-s" href="#">Choose Starter</a></div>
    </article>
    <article class="pcard star reveal">
      <div class="badge2">Best Value</div>
      <h3>Pro</h3>
      <p>The core offer for serious, recurring users who want the full picture.</p>
      <div class="pricetag">€20.99<small>/mo</small></div>
      <ul>
        <li>All premium signals</li>
        <li>Full multi-league coverage</li>
        <li>Priority feature access</li>
        <li>Dedicated Telegram room</li>
      </ul>
